        "text": "I have not visited this hospital but I staying in neighbourhood. Atleast 4 to 5 times a day their Ambulance are moving with siren and emergency lights on but no patient is inside Ambulance.  I request Hospital Management to ensure that Ambulance emergency siren is on only when Ambulance is going for emergency and not has a Horn to get privilege on road.\n\nAs a citizen it is our responsibility to give preference to Ambulance and Ambulance driver should not misuse their privelage",
